			<h2>About</h2>
			<p>Call Me They is my graduation project at the Interactive/Media/Design department at <a target="_blank" href="http://www.kabk.nl/">The Royal Academy of Art</a>, the Hague. It is a response to my exploration of gender as a continuum rather than a binary. The installation allows for a myriad of possibilities from a simple set of imposed constraints. A room is covered in hooks and pieces of fabric are strung between them, creating an over-arching shape. The viewer may interact with the shape to alter and evolve it in an infinite number of ways.</p>
